import styled from 'styled-components'
import React from 'react'

const Container = styled.div`
    
`

function CategoryItem( { item } ) {
  return (
    <Container>
        
        <Image/>

        <Info>
            <Title> {item.Title} </Title>
            <Button>SHOP NOW</Button>
        </Info>

    </Container>
  )
}

export default CategoryItem
